* {{ill|Kibikido-nushi-no-kami|ja|気吹戸主神|lt=Kibikido-nushi-no-kami|lt_ja=氣吹戸主神|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kibikido-nushi-no-kami|qq=}}
* {{ill|Hayasasurabime-no-kami|ja|速佐須良比売神|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Hayasasurabime-no-kami|qq=}}
